name: Verify Underwriter Manager should be displayed next to Underwriter Name for Policy Reports

testSteps.description: 1: Verify Underwriter Manager should be displayed next to Underwriter Name for Policy Reports ({Reports=Suspended Policies})

children.description: Given underwriter is on home page of PAS
And select Reports 'Suspended Policies' from Policy
When user select Underwriting Overview 'Underwriting Overview' from VIEW
Then the field 'UNDERWRITER MANAGER' should be displayed next to 'UNDERWRITER NAME'
